{"type":"message","id":"f9f5eff2","parentId":"0f1192ae","timestamp":"2026-02-15T17:49:55.490Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Reflecting on Completion**\n\nI've successfully completed the tasks. The `docs/ACTIVE_CONTEXT.json` file is up-to-date, reflecting the current git state and hash. Furthermore, I've updated the `MASTER_PROTOCOL.md` and instantiated the `SkillOrchestrator` within `src/core/skill_orchestrator`.\n\n\n**Preparing the Final Report**\n\nNow I'm focusing on the final compilation. I will provide the context JSON, summarize the orchestrator logic, show the monitor script's status, and include the Rust function snippet. Before submitting, I'll execute the monitor script to ascertain its output. I'm aiming for accuracy, so that is my immediate concern.\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec_1771177795484_42","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python scripts/system_health_audit.py"},"thoughtSignature":""}],"api":"google-vertex","provider":"google-vertex","model":"gemini-3-pro-preview","usage":{"input":7440,"output":234,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":7674,"cost":{"input":0.014879999999999999,"output":0.002808,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.017688}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771177788560}}
